sm leading-relaxed font-sans\">Providing clean, sustainable and affordable energy to rural tribal communities through localized solar micro-grids. We light up households, schools, and health centers, paving the way for economic activity after sunset.</p><div class=\"grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 pt-4 border-t border-navy/5\"><div class=\"space-y-1\"><div class=\"flex items-center text-forest space-x-1.5\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-globe w-3.5 h-3.5 stroke-[2]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"M12 2a14.5 14.5 0 0 0 0 20 14.5 14.5 0 0 0 0-20\"></path><path d=\"M2 12h20\"></path></svg><span class=\"font-serif font-bold text-navy text-sm sm:text-base leading-none\">50+</span></div><span class=\"text-[9px] uppercase tracking-wider text-navy/40 font-semibold block\">Villages</span></div><div class=\"space-y-1\"><div class=\"flex items-center text-forest space-x-1.5\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-zap w-3.5 h-3.5 stroke-[2]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M4 14a1 1 0 0 1-.78-1.63l9.9-10.2a.5.5 0 0 1 .86.46l-1.92 6.02A1 1 0 0 0 13 10h7a1 1 0 0 1 .78 1.63l-9.9 10.2a.5.5 0 0 1-.86-.46l1.92-6.02A1 1 0 0 0 11 14z\"></path></svg><span class=\"font-serif font-bold text-navy text-sm sm:text-base leading-none\">5MW+</span></div><span class=\"text-[9px] uppercase tracking-wider text-navy/40 font-semibold block\">Solar Capacity</span></div><div class=\"space-y-1\"><div class=\"flex items-center text-forest space-x-1.5\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" s