parent\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 50vw\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fproject_delhi_medical.png&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fproject_delhi_medical.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fproject_delhi_medical.png&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fproject_delhi_medical.png&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fproject_delhi_medical.png&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fproject_delhi_medical.png&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fproject_delhi_medical.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fproject_delhi_medical.png&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fproject_delhi_medical.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fproject_delhi_medical.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-navy/30 via-transparent to-transparent\"></div><span class=\"absolute top-4 left-4 bg-white/95 backdrop-blur-sm text-navy text-[10px] uppercase font-bold tracking-widest px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full shadow-sm\">📍 <!-- -->Delhi</span><div class=\"absolute top-4 right-4 flex flex-wrap gap-1.5 max-w-[70%] justify-end\"><span class=\"bg-forest/80 backdrop-blur-sm text-white text-[9px] font-semibold tracking-wider px-2 py-1 rounded-full uppercase\">Healthcare</span><span class=\"bg-forest/80 backdrop-blur-sm text-white text-[9px] font-semibold tracking-wider px-2 py-1 rounded-full uppercase\">Community Development</span><span class=\"bg-forest/80 backdrop-blur-sm text-white text-[9px] font-semibold tracking-wider px-2 py-1 rounded-full uppercase\">Emergency Relief</span></div></div><div class=\"p-8 sm:p-10 space-y-6\"><h3 class=\"font-serif font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl text-navy group-hover:text-forest transition-colors duration-300\">Delhi Medical Checkup Initiative</h3><p class=\"text-navy/70 text-sm leading-relaxed font-sans\">Free health checkups, diagnostics, expert consultations, and essential medicine distribution for underserved urban slum communities in Delhi and nearby suburban clusters.</p><div class=\"grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 pt-4 border-t border-navy/5\"><div class=\"space-y-1\"><div class=\"flex items-center text-forest space-x-1.5\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-heart w-3.5 h-3.5 stroke-[2]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M2 9.5a5.5 5.5 0 0 1 9.591-3.676.56.56 0 0 0 .818 0A5.49 5.49 0 0 1 22 9.5c0 2.29-1.5 4-3 5.5l-5.492 5.313a2 2 0 0 1-3 .019L5 15c-1.5-1.5-3-3.2-3-5.5\"></path></svg><span class=\"font-serif font-bold text-navy text-sm sm:text-base leading-none\">20,000+</span></div><span class=\"text-[9px] uppercase tracking-wider text-navy/40 font-semibold block\">Beneficiaries</span></div><div class=\"space-y-1\"><div class=\"flex items-center text-forest space-x-1.5\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-activity w-3.5 h-3.5 stroke-[2]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M22 12h-2.48a2 2 0 0 0-1.93 1.46l-2.35 8.36a.25.25 0 0 1-.48 0L9.24 2.18a.25.25 0 0 0-.48 0l-2.35 8.36A2 2 0 0 1 4.49 12H2\"></path></svg><span class=\"font-serif font-bold text-navy text-sm sm:text-base leading-none\">100+</span></div><span class=\"text-[9px] uppercase tracking-wider text-navy/40 font-semibold block\">Health Camps</span></div><div class=\"space-y-1\"><div class=\"flex items-center text-forest space-x-1.5\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-globe w-3.5 h-3.5 stroke-[2]\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"M12 2a14.5 14.5 0 0 0 0 20 14.5 14.5 0 0 0 0-20\"></path><path d=\"M2 12h20\"></path></svg><span class=\"font-serif font-bold text-navy text-sm sm:text-base leading-none\">50+</span></div><span class=\"text-[9px] uppercase tracking-wider text-navy/40 font-semibold block\">Communities</span></div></div></div></div><div class=\"px-8 pb-8 sm:px-10 sm:pb-10 pt-2\"><button class=\"relative w-44 h-12 bg-navy text-white rounded-full p-1.5 overflow-hidden flex items-center justify-start shadow-md hover:scale-[1.03] transition-transform duration-300 group/btn cursor-pointer\"><div class=\"w-9 h-9 rounded-full bg-white text-navy flex items-center justify-center z-20 flex-shrink-0\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-arrow-right w-4 h-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M5 12h14\"></path><path d=\"m12 5 7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></div><span class=\"absolute right-6 font-semibold text-sm select-none z-10\">Read More</span></button></div></div></div></div></section><section id=\"classroom-transformation\" class=\"bg-white py-24 md:py-32\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 items-center mb-20\"><div class=\"lg:col-span-5 space-y-8\"><div class=\"space-y-4\"><span class=\"text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest text-forest uppercase block\">Classroom Transformation</span><h2 class=\"font-serif text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-navy leading-tight\">Changing Classrooms. Changing Lives.</h2><p class=\"text-navy/70 text-sm sm:text-base leading-relaxed\">We transform dark, under-resourced state schools into safe, modern, colorful and inspiring learning spaces for children to grow, study and learn.</p></div><div class=\"space-y-4\"><div class=\"flex items-start space-x-4 p-4 rounded-2xl border border-navy/5 bg-beige/10\"><div class=\"p-2 rounded-xl bg-forest/10 text-forest mt-0.5\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-building w-5 h-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12 10h.01\"></path><path d=\"M12 14h.01\"></path><path d=\"M12 6h.01\"></path><path d=\"M16 10h.01\"></path><path d=\"M16 14h.01\"></path><path d=\"M16 6h.01\"></path><path d=\"M8 10h.01\"></path><path d=\"M8 14h.01\"></path><path d=\"M8 6h.01\"></path><path d=\"M9 22v-3a1 1 0 0 1 1-1h4a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v3\"></path><rect x=\"4\" y=\"2\" width=\"16\" height=\"20\" rx=\"2\"></rect></svg></div><div><h4 class=\"font-serif font-bold text-navy text-base\">Better Infrastructure</h4><p class=\"text-xs text-navy/60 leading-relaxed mt-0.5\">Desks, smart-boards, leakage proof roofing, clean paint.</p></div></div><div class=\"flex items-start space-x-4 p-4 rounded-2xl border border-navy/5 bg-beige/10\"><div class=\"p-2 rounded-xl bg-forest/10 text-forest mt-0.5\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-graduation-cap w-5 h-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M21.42 10.922a1 1 0 0 0-.019-1.838L12.83 5.18a2 2 0 0 0-1.66 0L2.6 9.08a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.832l8.57 3.908a2 2 0 0 0 1.66 0z\"></path><path d=\"M22 10v6\"></path><path d=\"M6 12.5V16a6 3 0 0 0 12 0v-3.5\"></path></svg></div><div><h4 class=\"font-serif font-bold text-navy text-base\">Improved Learning</h4><p class=\"text-xs text-navy/60 leading-relaxed mt-0.5\">Modern activitykits, science labs, high-quality reference books.</p></div></div><div class=\"flex items-start space-x-4 p-4 rounded-2xl border border-navy/5 bg-beige/10\"><div class=\"p-2 rounded-xl bg-forest/10 text-forest mt-0.5\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-flame w-5 h-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M12 3q1 4 4 6.5t3 5.5a1 1 0 0 1-14 0 5 5 0 0 1 1-3 1 1 0 0 0 5 0c0-2-1.5-3-1.5-5q0-2 2.5-4\"></path></svg></div><div><h4 class=\"font-serif font-bold text-navy text-base\">Bright Futures</h4><p class=\"text-xs text-navy/60 leading-relaxed mt-0.5\">A positive environment that cuts dropout rates by 80%.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"lg:col-span-7 space-y-4\"><div class=\"relative aspect-[16/10] w-full rounded-3xl overflow-hidden border border-navy/10 shadow-lg cursor-ew-resize select-none\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 w-full h-full\"><img alt=\"Modern transformed classroom with bright desks and paint\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" class=\"object-cover\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 50vw\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fclassroom_after.png&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fclassroom_after.png&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fclassroom_after.png&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fclassroom_after.png&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fclassroom_after.png&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fclassroom_after.png&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fclassroom_after.png&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fclassroom_after.png&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fclassroom_after.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fassets%2Fclassroom_after.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\"/><span class=\"absolute bottom-4 right-4 bg-emerald-600/90 text-white text-[9px] uppercase font-bold t