4 7h16\"></path><path d=\"m16 21 4-4-4-4\"></path><path d=\"M20 17H4\"></path></svg></div></div></div><div class=\"flex justify-between items-center text-[10px] uppercase font-semibold text-navy/40 tracking-wider px-2\"><span>← Drag Slider to Compare →</span><span>Visual Progress</span></div></div></div><div class=\"border-t border-navy/10 pt-12\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6\"><div class=\"text-center md:text-left\"><div class=\"font-serif font-bold text-3xl sm:text-4xl text-forest mb-1\">120+</div><div class=\"text-[10px] sm:text-xs text-navy/50 font-bold uppercase tracking-wider\">Classrooms Transformed</div></div><div class=\"text-center md:text-left\"><div class=\"font-serif font-bold text-3xl sm:text-4xl text-forest mb-1\">35,000+</div><div class=\"text-[10px] sm:text-xs text-navy/50 font-bold uppercase tracking-wider\">Students Benefited</div></div><div class=\"text-center md:text-left\"><div class=\"font-serif font-bold text-3xl sm:text-4xl text-forest mb-1\">25+</div><div class=\"text-[10px] sm:text-xs text-navy/50 font-bold uppercase tracking-wider\">Schools Upgraded</div></div><div class=\"text-center md:text-left\"><div class=\"font-serif font-bold text-3xl sm:text-4xl text-forest mb-1\">15</div><div class=\"text-[10px] sm:text-xs text-navy/50 font-bold uppercase tracking-wider\">Districts Impacted</div></div></div></div></div></section></main><footer class=\"bg-navy text-white pt-16 pb-8 border-t border-white/5\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-12 mb-16\"><div class=\"lg:col-span-2 flex flex-col space-y-6\"><a class=\"flex items-center space-x-2.5\" href=\"/\"><div class=\"w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-forest flex items-center justify-center text-white border border-white/20\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stro